    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a senior marketing strategist.\n\nAnalyze this competitor insight and generate 3 specific, \nactionable marketing recommendations.\n\nInsight: {{ $json.Insight }}\nTopic: {{ $json.Topic }}\nEngagement Level: {{ $json.Engagement_Level }}\nSummary: {{ $json.Summary }}\n\nReturn ONLY a raw JSON array. No markdown, no backticks, \nno explanation. Start with [ and end with ]:\n\n[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Specific action title here\",\n    \"rationale\": \"Why this will work based on the insight\",\n    \"category\": \"Content|SEO|Paid|Social|Email|Brand\",\n    \"priority\": \"High|Medium|Low\",\n    \"ice_score\": 75,\n    \"owner_role\": \"Content Manager|Social Media|CMO|Designer\",\n    \"due_days\": 14,\n    \"source_insight\": \"{{ $json.Topic }}\"\n  }\n]",
        "options": {
